	signable or decryptable That adds GNUTLS_PKCS11_OBJ_FLAG_MARK_NO_DECRYPT and
	GNUTLS_PKCS11_OBJ_FLAG_MARK_NO_SIGN which can be set during
	generation or write of keys.

