	* NEWS: doc update

2014-05-04  Nikos Mavrogiannopoulos <nmav@gnutls.org>

	* lib/ext/srp.c: initialize to null the SRP extension data on
	allocation.  Issue identified using valgrind and the Codenomicon TLS test suite.

