2014-02-13  Nikos Mavrogiannopoulos <nmav@redhat.com>

	* lib/includes/gnutls/x509.h, lib/libgnutls.map, lib/pkix.asn,
	lib/pkix_asn1_tab.c, lib/x509/Makefile.am, lib/x509/extensions.c,
